{"tid":1288149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國客憂被遊行人士攻擊　日後或減少來港","createTime":"2019-07-05T13:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T15:06:43.000Z","uid":41404,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e521aa02a69e06b879e7c6b70b9f3dba39ecbb5","tid":1288149,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"政府修訂《逃犯條例》引起連串示威，有網民發起於後日(7日)舉行「九龍區大遊行」，將途經尖沙咀及廣東道到高鐵西九龍站。有旅客相信遊行會和平進行，不擔心影響行程，但有中國旅客表明感無奈，指自己深愛香港，不明白為何會來港消費會受到被攻擊威脅。<br />\n<br />\n深圳旅客郭小姐表示，平常愛來港旅遊、購物及享受美食，認為沒有作侵害香港事情，直言若因此受到攻擊會感到無奈，「好像你喜歡一個人，但他打你嘴巴」，又認為大家是同胞，遊行沒必要，並直指香港近年變得激進，特別是個別人士，如學生。<br />\n<br />\n同行的丁小姐亦指，對人身安全感擔心，來港消費是抱開心心情，但若因而被打或受傷，必然會影響她對香港形象，而後日必定不會到廣東道一帶購物，甚至日後亦會減少來港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190705/bkn-20190705170746104-0705_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190705%2Fbkn-20190705170746104-0705_00822_001.html&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHTrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=ec556cc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190705/bkn-20190705170746104-0705_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a0c65e32764c9694bc7971a31e6a0c84bd218cba","tid":1288149,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:29:19.000Z","msg":"唔好黎<br />\n再黎被天收"},{"pid":"419615d31368933869b47cc6e09e349e5b226cdb","tid":1288149,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"好吖<br />\n最好港爆<br />\n點解呢度d 樓要比你14億蝗蟲買？<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/FqbFZAW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqbFZAW.gif&h=84c95dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/FqbFZAW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqbFZAW.gif&h=84c95dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https: